document_data.mainbody:
House Teyachumet was a deceased drow house of Ched Nasad.
House Teyachumet was destroyed more than a century before 1366 DR (that is, sometime before 1266 DR). Bregan Daerthe was likely involved in the houses downfall.
 Rai-guy Bondalek Former house member. Wizard and high priest of Lolth, later lieutenant of Bregan Daerthe.
